        "description": {
            "value": "<p><strong>Trigger</strong> A creature in range Strides</p>\n<hr />\n<p>You surround a moving creature with lifelike illusions, shifting their perception of the terrain to subtly lead them off course. The target must attempt a Will save. Regardless of the result, the creature is immune to lose the path for 1 hour.</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Success</strong> The creature is unaffected.</p>\n<p><strong>Failure</strong> The creature treats all squares as difficult terrain for its Stride.</p>\n<p><strong>Critical Failure</strong> As failure, except that you determine where the target moves during the Stride, though you can't move it into hazardous terrain or to a place it can't stand.</p>"
